  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK906">
<l>imaiyāriṉ vāḻiṉum pāṭilarē yillāḷ</l>
<l>amaiyārtō ḷañcu pavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They that fear the bamboo-like shoulders of their wives will be destitute of manliness though they may flourish like the Gods.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
